    text: "The 'Mountain-Sea Change' spirit means that it is bad to repeat the same thing several times when fighting the enemy. There may be no help but to do something twice, but do not try it a third time. If the enemy thinks of the mountains, attack like the sea; and if he thinks of the sea, attack like the mountains.",
